                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-255-off1305 t18170917-255-crimeloc1308"></join>. On the 5th of August I was in bed-my chest had the key in it. About three o'clock in the morning I heard some person running along the deck; I got up, ran on deck, and found the bundle by the bowsprit, and the prisoner concealed under the bowsprit - I secured him. The bundle contained the articles stated in the indictment. The prisoner was quite a stranger.</p>
